Title: Everpure Claris water filter cartridge
Description: Removing harmful contaminants, the Everpure Claris water filter cartridge ensures that every cup of tea and coffee tastes great and is free of unpleasant odours. Using a clever five-stage filtration process, this cartridge offers pre-filtration before enacting its carbonate hardness adjustment and highly effective carbon block, all of which is in addition to a solid membrane block and fine filtration suitable for filtering out particles as small as five microns.

Title: Aqua Cure Hydro+ water filter cartidge
